data.description: AFFORDABLE 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 1 Car Garage Manufactured home situated on an OVERSIZED 0.49 acre lot in North Fort Myers. NO HOA FEES & NO FLOOD REQUIRED!  The living room offers plenty of space for entertaining. The kitchen comes with plenty of cabinet space with a stove top and refrigerator and in kitchen dining space. The master bedroom is spacious with a private bathroom with walk-in shower. With a little TLC, this property has the potential to become a comfortable and cozy haven. The generous lot size offers endless possibilities for those looking to create their dream space.  Schedule your showing TODAY!
